16 public interest. To this end, this Section provides the procedure for judicial
17 resolution of claims for environmental damage to property arising from activities
18 subject to the jurisdiction of the Department of Conservation and Energy, office of
19 conservation. The provisions of this Section shall be implemented upon receipt of
